hits.definition:
举 (F 舉)

[jǔ] raise;

    举行 jǔxíng hold (a meeting);

    选举 xuǎnjǔ election;

    举例 jǔlì give an example

客

[kè] (= 客人 kèrén) guest;

    客观 kèguān objective;

    客气 kèqi polite

证 (F 證, 証)

[zhèng] prove;

    图书证 túshūzhèng library card;

    签证 qiānzhèng visa

苦

[kǔ] bitter;

    艰苦 jiānkǔ arduous;

    痛苦 tòngkǔ suffering

注

[zhù] pour, (F 註) notes;

    注意 zhùyì pay attention;

    注视 zhùshì gaze

费 (F 費)

[fèi] cost;

    学费 xuéfèi tuition

足

[zú] foot, (= 足够 zúgòu) enough;

    满足 mǎnzú satisfy

尔 (F 爾)

[ěr] <archaic> you;

    尔后 ěrhòu thereafter;

    高尔夫 gāo'ěrfū golf

招

[zhāo] beckon, recruit, attract;

    招待 entertain (guests)

晚

[wǎn] late;

    晚上 wǎnshang evening;

    夜晚 yèwǎn night;

    晚饭 wǎnfàn dinner
